{"tid":719672,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭被逐出歐戰兩年","createTime":"2018-06-27T15:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T15:49:31.000Z","uid":20634,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"50496e18ac7de47c27ab6601ad52cf88e7165559","tid":719672,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"北京時間6月27日晚，歐足聯官方宣布對AC米蘭俱樂部處以兩年歐戰禁賽，歐足聯認為他們不尊重財政公平法案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/1D/37/ChOxM1szpfuAUankAAEM7dO_NlY733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F1D%2F37%2FChOxM1szpfuAUankAAEM7dO_NlY733.jpg&h=73b5177b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俱樂部財務控制機構審判分庭(CFCB)認定，AC米蘭俱樂部違反歐足聯俱樂部許可以及財政公平法案，尤其違反了財政收支平衡的要求。AC米蘭因此被禁止參加2018-19及2019-20賽季的歐戰比賽。<br />\n<br />\n歐足聯表示，AC米蘭可以向體育仲裁法庭上訴。<br />\n<br />\n據意大利媒體稱，亞特蘭大將遞補參加歐聯正賽，佛羅倫薩則將獲得歐聯淘汰賽資格"},{"pid":"1c442547aab375a7a14643a2882706c45085d3c7","tid":719672,"uid":35331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f3b45d8038c22f7d1803a09a0f170a22877af2","tid":719672,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c539f5cfaa8e081b33a3f95c7fb3928df33456","tid":719672,"uid":16067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩呀dllm"},{"pid":"f87312ab72da06efc743de2d92783dfc6c678529","tid":719672,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:16:40.000Z","msg":